Sassi against the feretro, screams, threats against the religious, and there was also those who tried to reach the chariot to throw the psalm in the Tiber: the witnesses tell, in the Roman night illuminated by the torchlights and the fires of the appetizers, of an atmosphere from pure Middle Ages.
